{"tid":126739,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張 紋 嘉 想 嫁 外 國 人","createTime":"2017-02-19T14:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T14:42:16.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af10df699fbd278f84eacb86a298782594634867","tid":126739,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"張紋嘉（Crystal）、賈思樂、林漪娸同廖安麗噚日喺石硤尾一間中學出席「身前行動」舉辦嘅學校巡迴話劇演出。Crystal以劇團製作人身份返母校，宣揚珍惜生命訊息，「現今學生壓力大，希望大家珍惜生命，劇中會邀請學生上台參演。」Crystal話跟公司約滿後，計劃到美國發展，並笑言：「仍然會喺香港拍電視、電影、做舞台劇，我都想嫁個外國人。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170215/large/15ec4p9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170215%2Flarge%2F15ec4p9.jpg&h=71678e07&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}